title: Single cell RNA-seq analysis of IDH-mutant astrocytoma
abstract: To understand the diversity of expression states within IDH-mutant astrocytoma tumors, we profiled 6341 cells from 10 tumors by single cell RNA-seq
overall_design:
Tumors were disaggregated, sorted into single cells, and profiled by Smart-seq2.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
**Submitter declares reads will be made available through controlled access SRA and/or dbGaP.**
